OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'endearing' man
OL,4,Cafter remains found across city
OL,6,FThe family of an 'endearing' man whose
OL,7,Fremains have been found in four
OL,8,Fdifferent locations have thanked the
OL,9,Fpublic for their "overwhelming"
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FStuart Everett, 67, is thought to have
OL,13,Fdied at an address in the Winton area
OL,14,Fof Manchester at the end of March
OL,15,Fbefore parts of his body were
OL,16,Fdiscovered in four different areas.
OL,18,FTwo men have been charged with
OL,19,FStuart's murder and have appeared in
OL,20,Fcourt.
