OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'endearing' man
OL,4,Cafter remains found across city
OL,6,FIn a statement issued through (GMP),
OL,7,Fhis family said they were "united in
OL,8,Fgrief".
OL,10,F"We as a family are united in our
OL,11,Fgrief over the devastating news of
OL,12,FStuart's untimely death and the manner
OL,13,Fin which he died," the family said.
OL,15,F"He was a unique and endearing
OL,16,Fcharacter who always put his family
OL,17,Fand many friends first.
