OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'endearing' man
OL,4,Cafter remains found across city
OL,6,F"He loved his food, his garden, his
OL,7,Fmusic and a flutter on the horses, we
OL,8,Fhave been overwhelmed with the
OL,9,Fmessages of support and are thankful
OL,10,Fthat so many people thought so much of
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,F"He did not deserve to die the way he
OL,14,Fdid and will be eternally missed. RIP."
OL,16,FPolice said Mr Everett was local to
OL,17,Fthe area.
OL,19,FOn Monday, Michal Jaroslaw Polchowski,
OL,20,F68, and Marcin Majerkiewicz, 42, were
OL,21,Fcharged with murder.
