OL,6,FMr Everett's remains had been wrapped
OL,7,Fin clear plastic and were discovered
OL,8,Fby a passer-by on 4 April.
OL,10,FRemains were also found at two more
OL,11,Flocations on 27 and 28 April, and on
OL,12,FMonday 30 April morning police said
OL,13,Fthere had been a further discovery in
OL,14,Fan alleyway close to railway lines off
OL,15,FWorsley Road.
