OL,6,FPolchowski and Majerkiewicz, both of
OL,7,FWorsley Road, Eccles, were remanded in
OL,8,Fcustody after appearing at Manchester
OL,9,FCrown Court and will next appear in
OL,10,Fcourt on 18 July for a plea and trial
OL,11,Fpreparation hearing.
OL,13,FA provisional trial date of 3 March
OL,14,F2025 was fixed by Judge Nicholas Dean
OL,15,FKC, the Honorary Recorder of
OL,16,FManchester.
