OL,6,FGMP says it is continuing searches
OL,7,Facross Salford at sites at Blackleach
OL,8,FReservoir, Linneyshaw Colliery Wood,
OL,9,FBridgewater Canal, and a house in
OL,10,FWinton.
OL,12,FThe force also remains at a warehouse
OL,13,Fin Bury.
OL,15,FIt added: "We're continuing to receive
OL,16,Fdetails from the public that may
OL,17,Fassist our searches.
OL,19,F"Any further information should be
OL,20,Fgiven to us by calling 101 and quoting
OL,21,Flog number 2695 of 4 April 2024.
